column1: # 1881 figures omitted - all are bracketed and the sheet says they are estimates.
# Corrected two transcription errors in 1921 column.
# Corrected 1939 Total which had been added incorrectly (0.01 error).
# The October 1943 figure is identified as part-estimate on the sheet and has been retained.
# The site is Cherry Hill House on Bishopsgate Street.
# A note on the 1930s sheet (added in 1942) casts doubt on the 1939 and 1940 figures.
# It says that the amounts are reasonable (apart from September 1939) if they are multipled by 1.61.
